ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectEx-Gratia Payment - Canadian Coast Guard Auxiliary
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Canadian Heritage to make a one-time EX-GRATIA PAYMENT of $50,000.00 to the CANADIAN COAST GUARD AUXILIARY on behalf of Their Royal Highnesses The Duke and Duchess of Cambridge on the occasion of their wedding.
